room_title: Escape room "Gold Rush" by The Escape Game Pigeon Forge in Pigeon Forge
room_address: 131 Island Drive, Suite 9139 Pigeon Forge, TN 37863
room_description: For nearly two centuries, the hope of gold has lured people to the hills of Northern California. No one was captivated more than Clyde Hamilton, a greedy gold prospector who loved to gamble. Clyde made too many bets with the wrong crowd and now he’s missing. You’ve been tipped off to where he stashed his gold... but so has the mob. Find it first!
